Package com.williambarkoff.csx.riemann

Class for approximating the area under a curve
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractRiemann
    Class riemann represents a Riemann sum.
    LeftHandRule
    RightHandRule approximates the Riemann sum at the left of each subinterval.
    MaximumRule
    RightHandRule approximates the Riemann sum at the maximum point of each subinterval.
    MidpointRule
    RightHandRule approximates the Riemann sum at the midpoint of each subinterval.
    MinimumRule
    RightHandRule approximates the Riemann sum at the minimum point in each subinterval.
    RandomRule
    RandomRule approximates the Riemann sum at a random point on each subinterval.
    RiemannApp
    Riemann app is a runnable OpenSourcePhysics app that plots and computes multiple Riemann sums.
    RiemannWorker  
    RightHandRule
    RightHandRule approximates the Riemann sum at the right of each subinterval.
    TrapezoidRule
    Trapezoid rule uses a trapezoidal area to calculate the Riemann sum.
